{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"qA1wOFHTdkOq8ns8pAiwT","title":"审查对象","desc":"","updated":1649300546346,"created":1645500600551,"custom":{},"fname":"censorship.subjects","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"e4f5047a71e532a47e3b444db9a5ffdd","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"censorship.subjects","id":"qA1wOFHTdkOq8ns8pAiwT","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"censorship.platforms","alias":"平台","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":3,"offset":223},"end":{"line":11,"column":32,"offset":252},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"censorship.platforms"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"censorship.subjects","id":"qA1wOFHTdkOq8ns8pAiwT","vaultName":"vault"},"value":".subjects.calendar","alias":"敏感日期","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":28,"offset":435},"end":{"line":23,"column":57,"offset":464},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":".subjects.calendar"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"censorship.subjects","id":"qA1wOFHTdkOq8ns8pAiwT","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"censorship.collateraldamage","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":144,"offset":970},"end":{"line":31,"column":175,"offset":1001},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"censorship.collateraldamage"}}],"anchors":{"内容":{"type":"header","text":"内容","value":"内容","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2},"信息渠道":{"type":"header","text":"信息渠道","value":"信息渠道","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"技术":{"type":"header","text":"技术","value":"技术","line":19,"column":0,"depth":2},"语言":{"type":"header","text":"语言","value":"语言","line":23,"column":0,"depth":2},"日期":{"type":"header","text":"日期","value":"日期","line":27,"column":0,"depth":2},"内容形式":{"type":"header","text":"内容形式","value":"内容形式","line":31,"column":0,"depth":2},"事件":{"type":"header","text":"事件","value":"事件","line":39,"column":0,"depth":2},"在线知识":{"type":"header","text":"在线知识","value":"在线知识","line":48,"column":0,"depth":2},"领导人":{"type":"header","text":"领导人","value":"领导人","line":52,"column":0,"depth":2},"国家形态":{"type":"header","text":"国家形态","value":"国家形态","line":56,"column":0,"depth":2},"审查者本身指令":{"type":"header","text":"审查者本身指令","value":"审查者本身指令","line":67,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["JmkwI8RhQM1w3hyC2BJeH","l0m9w898rzd6esgxpa0w9ne","hlx9isc0jvv6qmzo8by99lz","SYYEQDx0b8EddBehDADxU","Zwk7U7IT9j7Z7n71EiDWb","ofqya32512pt1985hsxuk7c","kvjlz6q9wd22g6l2kbs0s5a","jjdav0mqxkc8sdi3rj89st3"],"parent":"qAItL5nac0TIpD7Uv7eB5","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"审查对象\">审查对象<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#审查对象\"></a></h1>\n<p>审查针对的目标通常是信息载体，包括图书、影视，也会有音乐等，但是在很多时候，资源/人和社会群体也会成为审查者的攻击目标。审查者通常关注信息的获取者获得的信息内容，但是为了节约成本，也常常直接切断信息的传播渠道，不一而足。</p>\n<h2 id=\"内容\">内容<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#内容\"></a></h2>\n<p>色情是审查者经常用来合法化审查的理由，但是在中国，色情内容的审查反倒是次要的，政治性的内容和自由的言论才是重点。例如在一些网站被网友发现有儿童色情的内容并投诉后，根本没有人理会。</p>\n<h2 id=\"信息渠道\">信息渠道<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#信息渠道\"></a></h2>\n<p>各种<a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/By8DfRV0qx4GKXD61L5jM\">平台</a> 都是审查者骚扰的对象。</p>\n<h2 id=\"技术\">技术<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#技术\"></a></h2>\n<p>很多工具网站，尽管和内容无关，但是因为可能帮助用户翻墙或传播信息，自然被审查者顾忌，而将其网站或关键字放入防火长城的屏蔽范围。</p>\n<h2 id=\"语言\">语言<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#语言\"></a></h2>\n<p>虽然对英文网站访问的限制并没有对中文网站那么严格，但是也有大批外文网站被长期封闭。比较典型的例子是维基百科。</p>\n<h2 id=\"日期\">日期<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#日期\"></a></h2>\n<p>在中国，很多日期因为历史事件而成为审查者每年特别关注的<a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">敏感日期 (Private)</a>。最敏感的日期应当是6月4日。</p>\n<h2 id=\"内容形式\">内容形式<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#内容形式\"></a></h2>\n<p>图书/影视剧/音乐<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/678251.html\">一直都是审查重点关注的对象</a>。</p>\n<p>音乐作为艺术形式，常常会表达创作者的政治立场，在世界各地都有不同的音乐家用音乐表达对时政的观点，当然在中国这是必然的禁区。早在2011年，中国文化文化部就发出一系列清理违规网络音乐产品的通告。歌手林宥嘉的《自然醒》等被列入名单。通告要求，“各搜索引擎、门户网站、行业网站、娱乐网站以及企业或个人网站，迅速开展自查自纠，一经发现自身网站提供有名单所列及的未经内容审查或备案的网络音乐产品，应当立即删除”（<a href=\"http://tech.sina.com.cn/i/2011-08-19/20145954854.shtml%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82\">http://tech.sina.com.cn/i/2011-08-19/20145954854.shtml）。</a></p>\n<p>2022年3月在俄罗斯侵略乌克兰期间，汇集全球影视节目的网站 imdb.com 遭到防火长城的封杀，有用户认为和国际演艺界（例如，<a href=\"https://twitter.com/safarier777/status/1501885094155661313\">本尼迪克特</a>）支持乌克兰人民而遇到<a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/2zuJ2qOYsmUKX4P0k3eRW\">连带伤害</a>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"事件\">事件<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#事件\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>俄乌战争</li>\n<li>丰县铁链女</li>\n<li>武汉肺炎</li>\n<li>天津大爆炸</li>\n<li>四川地震</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"在线知识\">在线知识<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#在线知识\"></a></h2>\n<p>在中国政府整顿课外教育产业之后，大量的在线教育/学习内容同时受到殃及，即使这些内容和商业无关。被用户戏称为“恶意自学”。</p>\n<h2 id=\"领导人\">领导人<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#领导人\"></a></h2>\n<p>因为外形相似于中国领导人习近平，华人歌唱家 Liu Keqing </p>\n<h2 id=\"国家形态\">国家形态<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#国家形态\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>日本</li>\n<li>辱华</li>\n<li>台湾</li>\n<li>香港</li>\n<li>新疆</li>\n<li>西藏</li>\n</ul>\n<p>“辱华”的范畴非常模糊和宽泛，也无人知道如何能够规避。网民大多戏称之以“乳滑”等。</p>\n<h2 id=\"审查者本身指令\">审查者本身指令<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#审查者本身指令\"></a></h2>\n<p>随着审查行为的延续，审查者和用户都会发现审查本身的指令会变成历史证据，所以也必须删除避免用户用来指责审查者。</p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/jjdav0mqxkc8sdi3rj89st3\">丑闻和社会事件</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/kvjlz6q9wd22g6l2kbs0s5a\">俄乌战争</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/JmkwI8RhQM1w3hyC2BJeH\">图书</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/SYYEQDx0b8EddBehDADxU\">影视剧</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/l0m9w898rzd6esgxpa0w9ne\">敏感日期</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/ofqya32512pt1985hsxuk7c\">武汉肺炎</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/hlx9isc0jvv6qmzo8by99lz\">灾难</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/censorshipgraph/notes/Zwk7U7IT9j7Z7n71EiDWb\">音乐</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"4isjXYVuLrirzEY6HxdBE","title":"墙国地图","desc":"","updated":1646712715590,"created":1644382378522,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"02c3c0c9e63ff90b668e6396d3f28d2a","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"4isjXYVuLrirzEY6HxdBE","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"underlying","alias":"实现方法","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":3,"offset":213},"end":{"line":12,"column":22,"offset":232},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"underlying"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"4isjXYVuLrirzEY6HxdBE","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"underlying","alias":"开源工具","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":3,"offset":382},"end":{"line":15,"column":24,"offset":403},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"underlying"}}],"anchors":{"如何使用审查地图":{"type":"header","text":"如何使用审查地图","value":"如何使用审查地图","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["vJRHPlmEzy8aoLmJq2EoS","qAItL5nac0TIpD7Uv7eB5","lFNqSJwuUdJJM9syQlMLP","4s98naE7Vp8rLwaBGAoRU","9mBvciCymZgzfdO2sVbde","EW05BFjl1ivR37Yv0wBIM","rTDV3gbrzSF4qbFVVLaPk"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n![](/assets/images/logo.png)\n\n墙国地图是社群共同贡献和维护的开源项目，目的是保存中国审查体系的来龙去脉，审查影响到的方方面面，人们的反制以及各种相关联的事件。\n\n因为采用了一种开放设计的机制，这个地图的版本将不断迭代并随时向贡献者发放特别的激励，所以你也可以加入并成为其中的一部分。\n\n## 如何使用审查地图\n\n审查地图是一个开源项目，你可以按图索骥，也可以补充完善，或者与更多人分享。\n\n- [[实现方法|underlying]]     \n- [源代码](https://github.com/China-Digital-Times-CDT/censorshipgraph)\n- [讨论](https://github.com/China-Digital-Times-CDT/censorshipgraph/issues)\n- [[开源工具 | underlying]]\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNote":{"init